jokes.content:
What do you call a radio in a refrigerator? 
Cool music

__What's a pirates favourite letter?__
You may think its R but their true love is the C.

__What's a pirate's least favourite letter?__
Dear sir,
Your internet access has been terminated due to illegal usage.
Sincerely, your service provider.

Mom finds a large number of BDSM magazines beneath her sons bed. Calls her husband up to the room to show him and discuss. "What do you think we should do?" she asks. Father frowns and responds "Well I guess spanking him is out of the question"
Rick Astley will let you borrow any of his Pixar collection DVDs but he will never give you Up

Who keeps the ocean clean?
The mermaid

Why did the condom fly across the room?
It got pissed off.

What do you call a singing laptop?
A Dell!

What do you do with a blue whale?
Cheer him up!

How does the ocean say hello?
It waves
